Class MatrixHeapArrayM2x2D

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.jtensors.MatrixHeapArrayM2x2D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Matrix2x2DType, MatrixReadable2x2DType, MatrixReadableDType, MatrixWritable2x2DType, MatrixWritableDType

    public final class MatrixHeapArrayM2x2D
extends Object
implements Matrix2x2DType

    The default implementation of the Matrix2x2DType interface.

    This implementation stores values in a plain on-heap array.

    Since:
    7.0.0
